    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But you won't get your new sled if she's dead.",
      "zh": "但如果她死了，你就拿不到新雪橇了。",
      "ja": "でも彼女が死んだら新しいそりはもらえないよ。",
      "time": "00:04:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sometimes I really don't like you.",
      "zh": "有時我真的不喜歡你。",
      "ja": "時々本当に君が嫌いだ。",
      "time": "00:04:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hold up! We're coming!",
      "zh": "等等！我們來了！",
      "ja": "待って！今行く！",
      "time": "00:04:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I mean, turn!",
      "zh": "我是說，轉彎！",
      "ja": "つまり、曲がって！",
      "time": "00:04:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How much you tag along?",
      "zh": "你要跟多久？",
      "ja": "どれくらい付き合うの？",
      "time": "00:04:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Anna, Elsa.",
      "zh": "安娜，艾莎。",
      "ja": "アナ、エルサ。",
      "time": "00:04:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Bad time soon.",
      "zh": "很快就會有麻煩。",
      "ja": "すぐに悪い時が来る。",
      "time": "00:05:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Uh-oh! The princess is trapped in the snowgoblins evil spell!",
      "zh": "糟糕！公主被雪妖的邪惡魔法困住了！",
      "ja": "やばい！姫が雪のゴブリンの呪いにかかった！",
      "time": "00:05:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Who else are? Make a prince!",
      "zh": "還有誰？變成王子！",
      "ja": "他には？王子を作れ！",
      "time": "00:05:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I've got you one!",
      "zh": "我有一個給你！",
      "ja": "一人いるよ！",
      "time": "00:05:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh no! The princess trapped too!",
      "zh": "哦不！公主也被困住了！",
      "ja": "ああ、姫も捕まった！",
      "time": "00:05:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Who cares about danger when there's love.",
      "zh": "有愛就不怕危險。",
      "ja": "愛があれば危険なんて気にしない。",
      "time": "00:05:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Anna, look!",
      "zh": "安娜，看！",
      "ja": "アナ、見て！",
      "time": "00:05:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Shizzing on the save of the forest.",
      "zh": "在森林的救援中奔跑。",
      "ja": "森を救うために走っている。",
      "time": "00:05:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The long spares cry out.",
      "zh": "長矛呼喊著。",
      "ja": "長い槍が叫ぶ。",
      "time": "00:05:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Boo!",
      "zh": "嘘！",
      "ja": "ばあ！",
      "time": "00:05:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What's on his draft make?",
