    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why are you hanging off the earth like a bat?",
      "zh": "你為什麼像蝙蝠一樣掛在地球上？",
      "ja": "なぜ地球にコウモリみたいにぶら下がってるの？",
      "time": "00:07:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All right.",
      "zh": "好吧。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:07:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait one second.",
