    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, almost.",
      "zh": "嗯，差不多。",
      "ja": "まあ、ほぼね。",
      "time": "00:07:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Was like my whole life got burned upside down.",
      "zh": "就像我的整個人生被顛覆了。",
      "ja": "まるで人生がひっくり返ったみたいだ。",
      "time": "00:07:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, whoo!",
      "zh": "哦，呼！",
      "ja": "おお、ふう！",
      "time": "00:07:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "zh": "對不起。",
      "ja": "ごめんね。",
      "time": "00:07:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I-I've had it.",
      "zh": "我受夠了。",
      "ja": "もう我慢できない。",
      "time": "00:07:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you okay?",
      "zh": "你還好嗎？",
      "ja": "大丈夫？",
      "time": "00:07:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you kidding me?",
      "zh": "你在開玩笑嗎？",
      "ja": "冗談でしょ？",
      "time": "00:07:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am wonderful.",
      "zh": "我很好。",
      "ja": "私は素晴らしいよ。",
      "time": "00:07:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I've always wanted to know.",
      "zh": "我一直想知道。",
      "ja": "ずっと知りたかった。",
      "time": "00:07:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's like you need to be me, you and the court.",
      "zh": "就像你需要成為我，你和宮廷。",
      "ja": "まるで君が私になり、君と宮廷がいるみたいだ。",
      "time": "00:07:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "何？",
      "time": "00:07:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey, whoa.",
      "zh": "嘿，哇。",
      "ja": "おい、わあ。",
      "time": "00:07:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, I love it even more.",
      "zh": "哦，我更喜歡了。",
      "ja": "ああ、もっと好きになった。",
      "time": "00:07:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All right. Let's start this thing over.",
      "zh": "好吧，我們重新開始。",
      "ja": "よし、もう一度始めよう。",
      "time": "00:08:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hi, everyone.",
      "zh": "大家好。",
      "ja": "みんな、こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:08:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm Olaf.",
      "zh": "我是奧拉夫。",
      "ja": "私はオラフです。",
      "time": "00:08:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And I like warm hugs.",
      "zh": "我喜歡溫暖的擁抱。",
      "ja": "そして私は暖かいハグが好き。",
      "time": "00:08:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Olaf?",
      "zh": "奧拉夫？",
      "ja": "オラフ？",
      "time": "00:08:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's right. Olaf.",
      "zh": "沒錯，奧拉夫。",
      "ja": "そうだよ、オラフ。",
      "time": "00:08:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Elsa?",
      "zh": "艾莎？",
      "ja": "エルサ？",
      "time": "00:08:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's me.",
      "zh": "是我。",
      "ja": "私だよ。",
      "time": "00:08:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Anna?",
      "zh": "安娜？",
      "ja": "アナ？",
      "time": "00:08:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "何？",
      "time": "00:08:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Anna?",
      "zh": "安娜？",
      "ja": "アナ？",
      "time": "00:08:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wow.",
      "zh": "哇。",
      "ja": "わあ。",
      "time": "00:08:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Elsa, you look different.",
      "zh": "艾莎，你看起來不一樣了。",
      "ja": "エルサ、君は違って見える。",
      "time": "00:08:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's a good different.",
      "zh": "這是好的不同。",
      "ja": "それは良い違いだ。",
      "time": "00:08:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And there's place in it.",
      "zh": "裡面有個地方。",
      "ja": "その中に場所がある。",
      "time": "00:08:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's amazing.",
      "zh": "真是太棒了。",
      "ja": "素晴らしい。",
      "time": "00:08:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝你。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:08:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I never knew what I was capable of.",
      "zh": "我從不知道自己有什麼能力。",
      "ja": "自分に何ができるか知らなかった。",
      "time": "00:08:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I love you.",
      "zh": "我愛你。",
      "ja": "愛してる。",
      "time": "00:08:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, my God.",
      "zh": "哦，我的天啊。",
      "ja": "ああ、神様。",
      "time": "00:08:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello, hello.",
      "zh": "哈囉，哈囉。",
      "ja": "こんにちは、こんにちは。",
      "time": "00:08:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What's happening where I was going?",
      "zh": "我去哪裡了，發生了什麼？",
      "ja": "どこに行ってたの？何が起きてる？",
      "time": "00:08:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm great.",
      "zh": "我很好。",
      "ja": "私は元気だよ。",
      "time": "00:09:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Actually.",
      "zh": "其實。",
      "ja": "実はね。",
      "time": "00:09:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Prince Hans of the Southern Isles.",
      "zh": "南方群島的漢斯王子。",
      "ja": "南の島々のハンス王子。",
      "time": "00:09:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I love you.",
      "zh": "我愛你。",
      "ja": "愛してる。",
      "time": "00:09:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I need to tell you about my past and where I'm from.",
      "zh": "我需要告訴你我的過去和來自哪裡。",
      "ja": "私の過去と出身を話さなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:09:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm losing.",
      "zh": "我正在失去。",
      "ja": "私は失っている。",
      "time": "00:09:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I do not know.",
      "zh": "我不知道。",
      "ja": "わからない。",
      "time": "00:09:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What are you reading, Majesty?",
      "zh": "陛下，你在讀什麼？",
      "ja": "陛下、何を読んでいるのですか？",
      "time": "00:09:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I've something to finish, author.",
      "zh": "我有事要完成，作者。",
      "ja": "終わらせることがあるんだ、作者。",
      "time": "00:09:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "zh": "對不起。",
      "ja": "ごめんなさい。",
      "time": "00:09:16"
    }
  ]
}